==================== Input ====================
# DIVERGENCE (prettier#15528): a blank line right after a node is preserved
# (normalized to one) for every node kind alike, and never invented.
- a
- b



# blank above is kept (and collapsed), even after a sequence
---
{ flow: mapping }

---
scalar doc


# blank above a trailing comment is kept for scalars too
---
literal: |
  text
# no blank is invented between a block scalar and this comment
---
last: value # trailing

# one blank stays one; Prettier doubles it when the final item
# has a trailing comment (the prettier#9130 shape, still alive there)

